data.description: Up to $10,000 in buyer's credit. This 1940's charmer is ready to find its new people! The 3-bedroom 1 bath 2 story home utilizes the space well sitting on a spacious .17-acre lot with a front deck and large back yard with irrigation available. This is a great starter home in a very convenient location. Ready to move in. Seller providing home warranty through July 2024. Buyer to do own due diligence on irrigation for the yard.
